  "context": "🔎INTEL\n========\n📌RALord Appeared with 2 Victims affecting Education and Engineering Sector 🇫🇷 🇦🇷\n📌RA Lord made their DLS more friendly, as sectors of the victims also mentioned in the Leak Site\n💡RA Lord started to advertise their recruitment on March 19, 2025 on a Forum\n📌RA Lord demands to code their encryptor using Python and Rust\n📌Fortinet, SonicWall, Cisco are targeted\n📌Bruteforcing and CVE Exploits are also welcomed by the group\n💡RALord Admin's username is \"ForLord\"\n📌Appends the file using .RALord extension and uses RC4 PRGA for Encryption\n📌Group uses Vanity TOR Domain Names for their DLS\n💡RA Lord Appeared recently, and RA World got shut down\n💡RA World also made use of Go File Storage to host their Samples\n💡RA World sample had been seen with 25% code match with FunkSec Ransomware and currently FunkSec Ransomware goes offline\n💡The group had revamped their site, by renaming it as \"RALord GBlog\"\n💡They also introduced new Onion for Affiliate Association called NOVA RaaS on April 1, 2025\n💡The group purposefully made a typo in word \"requast\" on NOVA platform, however recitified this mistake later\n💡The average time of Negotiation Window for each victim is 7 Days\n💡Added new victims: 🇹🇼 🇺🇸 🇪🇸 🇯🇵 🇳🇴 🇸🇦 🇫🇷\n💡Leaked files are hosted with MEGA platform, a file sharing service\n💡On 27th April, 2025; the group had made an announcement regarding their brand name change to \"NOVA\" and removing \"RALord\" from their business name. \n💡3 TOR Domains of NOVA had been listed\n💡In the new leak section in NOVA, the date of Encrypted and Published also listed by the group\n💡In May 2025; the group began to introduce Technical MCQ to access the portal. 2 Challenges shall be passed to access the portal. Wrong information leads to \"Script Kiddie\" page of Wikipeda\n💡Though after providing right answers, the site will get redirected to Script Kiddie Wiki Page after a Crypto Round: To calculate hex using XOR Operations; even after providing right answers\n💡In June 2025; the group had introduced 5 new TOR Domains\n💡Also introduced new Domain wit service called \"NOVA CLOUD\" to host compromised victim breach \n💡I exposed their real IP of NOVA CLOUD\n💡After my exposure, they migrated to new domain and also dropped their Ransomware Icon from the page\n💡In October 2025, found the leaks of a victim to be hosted on Go File Platform instead of their dedicated File Server\n💡Victims are advised to contact them on unique TOR Domains found on the Ransom Note, which are powered by \"Secure Chat\" service\n💡Data Leaks <100GB are hosted with Mega Cloud, and large leaks are hosted with their dedicated Onion File Servers\n💡The leaks hosted with Mega are auto-kicked as they violate privacy regulations\n📌Some samples appends \"ploja_NV\" after encryption\n💡In May 2026 (or prior), the group had added an AI Chat Support to the DLS Portal. But only a set of prepared questions are listed. This is another version of Summary in an AI form.\n📌Victim Count reached to 125\n💡Exposed 2 IPs associated with Nova Cloud Server\n📌AS23470 is notably used for Akira Ransomware 0-Day, Radar Ransomware, StegaBin - Malicious NPM package using Pastebin C2 North Korea\n📌AS46475 is notably used for CVE-2024-55956, Rimasuta Botnet, QAKBot\n💡Nova changed from RouterHosting to ReliableSite and LimeStone Networks to host their Cloud Server for Victim Leaks\n\nIOCs\n====\n\nMD5\nef846baabc14fe461cff4c4a0fd5056f\nbe15f62d14d1cbe2aecce8396f4c6289\n4566f5ba6d1a1db0dd7794ea8d791b3f\n66ca089cd347d18ae8ab200a4e7602a5\n45ac577dcbf721988b49768497ba3bb8\n826cc4ca915f9a49ec28b119a6655a5b\n4b93b2341974f36c9e464632e94d68b3\nc9f3f7a6a36a43c295afa2352c97d1c3\n\n\nDLS\n===\nnovadmrkp4vbk2padk5t6pbxolndceuc7hrcq4mjaoyed6nxsqiuzyyd.onion\nnovaxtychr6ohlc4zr5its73p6i7unpuhpwoodtzrg2y4w4seytatlid.onion\nralord3htj7v2dkavss2hjzviviwgsf4anfdnihn5qcjl6eb5if3cuqd.onion\nralordqe33mpufkpsr6zkdatktlu3t2uei4ught3sitxgtzfmqmbsuyd.onion\nralordt7gywtkkkkq2suldao6mpibsb7cpjvdfezpzwgltyj2la